1
00:00:01,634 --> 00:00:04,426
Previously on "Jojo's Bizarre Adventure"...

2
00:00:09,004 --> 00:00:09,717
What the?!

3
00:00:09,751 --> 00:00:11,971
Why am I a kid?!

4
00:00:12,103 --> 00:00:13,678
Pami!

5
00:00:14,012 --> 00:00:16,145
Little boy, are you all right there?

6
00:00:16,378 --> 00:00:19,129
I'll clean those wounds up and put some medicine on you.

7
00:00:24,883 --> 00:00:26,811
That's impossible!

8
00:00:27,419 --> 00:00:28,503
Chariot, help!

9
00:00:31,824 --> 00:00:33,615
Yes! Yes!

10
00:00:45,135 --> 00:00:47,327
