11
00:00:48,633 --> 00:00:48,893
Pami!

12
00:00:48,918 --> 00:00:51,080
I don't see that nice lady anywhere.

13
00:00:51,350 --> 00:00:54,203
Where'd she go? She couldn't have just vanished.

14
00:00:54,228 --> 00:00:55,923
She was sitting right behind me.

15
00:00:56,262 --> 00:00:59,370
