103
00:07:50,093 --> 00:07:52,528
Oh, no! I'm getting even smaller!

104
00:07:52,633 --> 00:07:53,614
Yahoo!

105
00:07:53,814 --> 00:07:55,058
Oh, boy!

106
00:07:55,083 --> 00:07:57,493
There's no way in hell I'm gonna lose now!

107
00:07:57,578 --> 00:07:59,421
