111
00:08:30,276 --> 00:08:31,016
Made it.

112
00:08:31,125 --> 00:08:34,400
Huh? Damn it. The stupid bars are too close together!

113
00:08:35,126 --> 00:08:36,979
Even a kid can't slip through.

114
00:08:38,238 --> 00:08:43,508
But I have to find a way to get out of here,
or that freak show's gonna kill us both! Crap!

115
00:08:46,683 --> 00:08:48,203
I-I can't cut them.

116
00:08:51,060 --> 00:08:53,081
This is just too good to be true.

117
00:08:53,127 --> 00:08:55,816
I see that your chariot has also become a toddler.

118
00:08:56,010 --> 00:08:58,542
The bars are too tough for its baby rapier.

119
00:08:58,593 --> 00:09:00,448
I bet it's gotten slower, too.

120
00:09:02,235 --> 00:09:05,009
Ready or not, here I come.

121
00:09:21,388 --> 00:09:25,128
Oh, Polnareff, here comes Alessi!

122
00:09:25,481 --> 00:09:26,435
Huh?

123
00:09:31,384 --> 00:09:32,913
H-he's gone.

124
00:09:32,954 --> 00:09:35,321
Huh? Where did he go?

125
00:09:35,403 --> 00:09:38,426
That brat. He just vanished.

126
00:09:38,807 --> 00:09:43,107
Or maybe the little spunk monkey found a
way to slither through the bars in the window.

127
00:09:47,041 --> 00:09:49,794
Clever, Polnareff. Very clever.

128
00:09:49,851 --> 00:09:52,204
You're trying to pull a fast one, aren't you?

129
00:09:52,890 --> 00:09:57,105
You think if you trick me into believing you
slipped through the window, it'll distract me.

130
00:09:57,150 --> 00:10:00,402
You must be hiding somewhere,
waiting to get the drop on me.

131
00:10:02,073 --> 00:10:03,750
Not bad, runt.

132
00:10:04,237 --> 00:10:07,598
Quite cunning indeed, for a miserable little shit!

133
00:10:07,844 --> 00:10:11,173
Polnareff, come out, come out, wherever you are.

134
00:10:12,874 --> 00:10:17,284
You're so puny now, you could easily
be hiding in that drawer over there.

135
00:10:17,489 --> 00:10:21,315
Yeah, he's probably hiding in the bucket or the drawer,

136
00:10:21,362 --> 00:10:25,368
