in that Teddy bear by the wall.

137
00:10:27,616 --> 00:10:29,017
Oh, where could he be?

138
00:10:29,090 --> 00:10:30,990
I've got a one-in-three chance.

139
00:10:31,383 --> 00:10:34,709
