like to get him with one swing.

140
00:10:34,742 --> 00:10:37,800
I'll crack open his infantile skull with this ax!

141
00:10:42,937 --> 00:10:46,908
I've decided you're tucking away
in that tattered, old Teddy bear!

142
00:10:47,892 --> 00:10:50,153
But my second guess is...

143
00:10:50,273 --> 00:10:51,881
This grandfather clock,

144
00:10:51,995 --> 00:10:54,041
the perfect hiding spot for a coward!

145
00:10:57,818 --> 00:11:00,182
I guess I was wrong.

146
00:11:01,570 --> 00:11:03,371
Then maybe he's...

147
00:11:03,396 --> 00:11:05,669
Hiding in this rusty bucket!

148
00:11:06,600 --> 00:11:07,230
But I...

149
00:11:10,214 --> 00:11:12,207
So you are in the bear!

150
00:11:14,160 --> 00:11:15,590
Then how about the drawer?!

151
00:11:17,695 --> 00:11:18,741
Where is he?!

152
00:11:18,862 --> 00:11:20,988
Where is he?! Where is he?! Where is he?! Where is he?!

153
00:11:21,022 --> 00:11:22,342
Where is he?!

154
00:11:23,305 --> 00:11:25,798
H-he's gone! But how?

155
00:11:26,104 --> 00:11:28,671
There's no way he could have gotten out of here!

156
00:11:29,050 --> 00:11:31,461
The walls, floor, and ceiling are all stone.

157
00:11:31,485 --> 00:11:34,858
Even if they were one centimeter
thick, chariot couldn't break through.

158
00:11:34,951 --> 00:11:36,858
And those bars are too narrow for him.

159
00:11:36,917 --> 00:11:38,557
I saw it with my own eyes.

160
00:11:38,793 --> 00:11:40,930
This is insane. Where is he?

161
00:11:40,975 --> 00:11:42,420
Where did he go?

162
00:11:45,479 --> 00:11:46,030
Huh?

163
00:11:46,489 --> 00:11:49,450
So you were outsmarted by a toddler, huh...

164
00:11:49,475 --> 00:11:50,029
What the...

165
00:11:50,382 --> 00:11:52,695
Old man Alessi.

166
00:12:02,376 --> 00:12:03,736
What's going on here?

167
00:12:03,783 --> 00:12:05,633
The goldfish just disappeared.

168
00:12:08,536 --> 00:12:09,029
Huh?

169
00:12:26,894 --> 00:12:29,220
I was hiding in the fish tank the whole time

170
00:12:29,490 --> 00:12:31,733
and used this mirror for camouflage.

171
00:12:31,758 --> 00:12:35,354
A kid could have figured out my
plan, and you totally fell for it!

172
00:12:35,429 --> 00:12:38,299
