Hey, get your ass back here!

178
00:13:01,266 --> 00:13:01,840
Pami!

179
00:13:01,864 --> 00:13:02,631
Hey, wait!

180
00:13:02,697 --> 00:13:05,719
Until you break your stand's
spell, I'm gonna keep attacking!

181
00:13:07,475 --> 00:13:09,438
Bad boy! Bad boy!

182
00:13:09,503 --> 00:13:12,327
You're such a bad boy!

183
00:13:12,527 --> 00:13:13,315
Of all the...

184
