229
00:15:37,671 --> 00:15:38,794
Guess I'm the winner.

230
00:15:38,846 --> 00:15:40,287
Hope you're watching, master Dio,

231
00:15:40,315 --> 00:15:42,267
'cause I'm about to kill Jotaro.

232
00:15:42,364 --> 00:15:45,530
You'd better give me a good reward
for everything I've gone through.

233
00:15:45,679 --> 00:15:49,163
Now, Jotaro, it's time to die!

234
00:15:51,131 --> 00:15:52,428
Whoa, what a hit.

235
00:15:52,552 --> 00:15:54,829
